{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-basic-personal-information/task-17","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 17","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kiswahili često koristi reči <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cuál</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cómo</span> da bi stvorio uobičajena pitanja.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál ... ?</span> se koristi za postavljanje pitanja <strong>specifičnih informacija</strong>, posebno pre glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span>. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nombre?</span> – Kako se zoveš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu número de teléfono?</span> – Koji je vaš broj telefona?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo ... ?</span> koristi se za pitanje <strong>kako</strong> nešto radi, piše se ili izgovara. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo te llamas?</span> – Kako se zoveš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo se escribe?</span> – Kako se piše?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio i dovršite rečenicu ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cuál</span> se koristi za traženje specifičnih informacija, posebno pre glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Es</span> potiče od glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span> i odgovara <span class=\"highlighted-text\">nacionalidad</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tu</span> to pokazuje da govornik pita jednu osobu.</p>\n<p>Ovo pitanje prati uobičajenu strukturu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu</span> + imenica? Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nombre?</span> - Kako se zoveš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nacionalidad?</span> - Kakvo je vaše državljanstvo?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ovde, Ángela pita specifične lične informacije: državljanstvo Estebana.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-basic-personal-information","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-basic-personal-information/task-17"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>¿BLANK es tu nacionalidad?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Cuál","feedback":"<p>Ova reč se koristi pre glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ser</span> za traženje specifičnih informacija. Uverite se da uključujete krugčić na slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">á</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"Ángela","position":{"x":50,"y":25,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_esteban_personal_records_dialogue_with_angela.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":33.26,"finishTimestamp":34.69},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Ángela","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Ángela","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.43,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Cuál es tu nacionalidad?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Ángela","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.93,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-basic-personal-information","dashedName":"task-17","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-basic-personal-details","modul